About.Name: Mohammed Al Rabey
About.Currently: Senior Eelectrical Engineering Student at SPU
About.AboutText: Hi, I am Mohammed Al Rabey. A senior  Electrical Engineering student at Seattle Pacific University. I love exploring technology and how it can change the world.I'm studying to understand how electronics work and how they're used in different industries.I'm excited to keep learning about things like how electricity moves and how digital devices work.I'm looking to meet people who share my interest in Electrical Engineering. I want to learn from experienced folks and grow in a fun and creative environment.If you have a position opening or would like to chat, please reach out to me at alrabeym@spu.edu.
